---
title: "US47 — Create / manage service listings"
---
sequenceDiagram
  actor A as Expert User
  participant B as «Boundary»<br/>ServicesScreen
  participant C as «Control»<br/>PublishService
  participant G as «Gateway»<br/>SupabaseGateway
  A->>B: create listing (price, format, response time)
  B->>C: publish(listing)
  C->>G: insert/update expert_services
  alt publish
    G-->>C: status = live
    B-->>A: visible in marketplace
  else archive
    G-->>C: status = archived
    B-->>A: hidden from marketplace
  end
